quote: Happiness is not something you postpone for the future; it is something you design for the present.
author: Jim Rohn

quote: The greatest happiness you can have is knowing that you do not necessarily require happiness.
author: William Saroyan

quote: Courage is not the absence of fear, but the triumph over it.
author: Nelson Mandela

quote: Courage is resistance to fear, mastery of fear, not absence of fear.
author: Mark Twain

quote: Being deeply loved by someone gives you strength while loving someone deeply gives you courage.
author: Lao Tzu

quote: Love is not finding someone to live with, it's finding someone you can't live without.
author: Rafael Ortiz

quote: Do not let the behavior of others destroy your inner peace.

quote: It's not what happens to you, but how you react to it that matters.

quote: Forgive yourself for not knowing what you didn't know before you learned it.
author: Maya Angelou

quote: Maybe there's more we all could have done, but we just have to let the guilt remind us to do better next time.

quote: Do not be embarrassed by your failures, learn from them and start again.

quote: The greatest wealth is health.

quote: The sun is a daily reminder that we too can rise again from the darkness, that we too can shine our own light.
author: S. Ajna

quote: If you change the way you look at things, the things you look at change.

quote: When anger arises, think of the consequences.

author: Mark Twain

quote: The greatest thing in the world is to know how to belong to oneself.
author: Michel de Montaigne
